Simply paste the following code on your <em>functions.php</em> file. If needed, you can add more file types by adding them on line 4, separated by a pipe (|)

只需要添加下面的代码到你的<em>functions.php 文件。 如果你还需要，你能添加文件类型到代码上的第4行 用(|)分开。
</em>
<pre>&lt;?php
function addUploadMimes($mimes) {
    $mimes = array_merge($mimes, array(
        'tmbundle|tmCommand|tmDragCommand|tmSnippet|tmLanguage|tmPreferences' =&gt; 'application/octet-stream'
    ));

    return $mimes;
}
?&gt;

add_filter('upload_mimes', 'addUploadMimes');
</pre>

You just have to paste the following code into your functions.php and  save the file. Once done, custom content will be inserted below each of  your posts.

你只需要添加下面的代码到你的functions.php 文件。 你定制的内容就会插入到每个文章的下面。
<pre>function add_post_content($content) {
	if(!is_feed() &amp;&amp; !is_home()) {
		$content .= '&lt;p&gt;This article is copyright &amp;copy; '.date('Y').'&amp;nbsp;'.bloginfo('name').'&lt;/p&gt;';
	}
	return $content;
}
add_filter('the_content', 'add_post_content');
</pre>

Simply paste this function on your <em>functions.php</em> file:

只需要添加下面的代码到你的<em>functions.php 文件
</em>
<pre>if ( !function_exists('edit_term_link') ) {
  function edit_term_link( $link = '', $before = '',
      $after = '', $term = null ) {

    if ( $term == null ) {
      global $wp_query;
      $term = $wp_query-&gt;get_queried_object();
    }

    $tax = get_taxonomy( $term-&gt;taxonomy );
    if ( !current_user_can($tax-&gt;cap-&gt;edit_terms) )
      return;

    if ( empty($link) )
      $link = __('Edit This');

    $link = '&lt;a href="' . get_edit_tag_link( $term-&gt;term_id,
        $term-&gt;taxonomy ) . '" title="' . $link . '"&gt;' . $link . '&lt;/a&gt;';
    echo $before .
       apply_filters( 'edit_term_link', $link, $term-&gt;term_id ) . $after;
  }
}
</pre>
Once you saved your <em>functions.php</em> file, add the following code on any category, tag or taxonomy template:

添加下面的代码到你想要编辑的 分类 标签 的模板上
<pre>&lt;?php edit_term_link(); ?&gt;</pre>
It will output a link (only if you're logged in as an administrator, of course) to quickly edit the term.

它将输出一个链接 到你的编辑页面 （当你是管理员登录时它才显示。

The first step is to paste the following code into your <em>functions.php</em> file:

第一步你要添加下面的代码到你的<em>functions.php文件</em>
<pre>function pdflink($attr, $content) {
	return '&lt;a href="http://docs.google.com/viewer?url=' . $attr['href'] . '"&gt;'.$content.'&lt;/a&gt;';
}
add_shortcode('pdf', 'pdflink');
</pre>
Once you saved the file, you'll be able to use the shortcode on your posts and page. Here is the syntax:

你能用类似下面的短代码添加到你的文章 或者页面。
<pre>[pdf href="http://yoursite.com/linktoyour/file.pdf"]View PDF[/pdf]</pre>
